title: Number of births in Sweden 2009 to 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of births, containing a total of 11 data points.
In general Number of births has stayed the same over the Year.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2010 and 2011.
Maximum Number of births, about 117425.0 was reported at Year 2016
Minimum Number of births about 111770.0 was reached at Year 2011
